# Laravel Soketi Integration

## When to use

- Setting up real-time broadcasting with Soketi WebSocket server
- Replacing Pusher with a self-hosted WebSocket solution
- Configuring Laravel Echo, channels, presence channels, and events
- Deploying Soketi with Docker, SSL, or in production

